  "format": "The new Sight & Sound poll lands mid-record. Sean and Amanda run down the Robert Downey Sr. documentary 'Sr.,' then build a first draft of the 2022 Best Picture top ten. Plus Sean's conversation with Laura Poitras about 'All the Beauty and the Bloodshed.'",
